snippet.title: The B.C. COVID-19 Vaccine Passports are here! New restrictions, no exemptions! O CANADA!
snippet.description:
THIS JUST IN! Starting September 13th, the unvaccinated people in the province of British Columbia, Canada will now be banned from various indoor activities including gyms, restaurants, movies, and so much more! NO MEDICAL OR RELIGIOUS EXEMPTIONS ALLOWED! When will we wake up from this nightmare?

♪ link to my song "CANCER" https://youtu.be/-EoF4OcmXdY ♪
